ll, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014129, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon you, O Aba Abdillah! You are Allah’s door of bestowal and acquisition. I testify that you spoke the truth, spoke truthfully, summoning the people to my master and yours, publicly and privately. I come to you as a pilgrim, entrusting you with my needs and now as I bid you farewell, I entrust you with my faith, my trust, the consequence of my deeds and all my hopes till the end of my life. Peace, divine mercy and His blessings be upon you. May Allah bless Muhammad and his family, the elite.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aap par salaam ho ay Abu Abdillah. Aap woh darwaaza hai jis se Khuda deta hai aur wahan se liya jaata hai, gawahi deta hu keh aap ne haq bayaan kiya aap ne hamesha sach bola aur mere aur apne Maula ki taraf bulaate rahe zaaheri wa poshida taur par, mai aaya hu aap ki ziyarat karne aur apni haajaat aap ke supurd (hawaale) karne ke liye, ab mai aap se wida hota hu aap ke supurd kiya mai ne apna deen apni amaanat apne amal ka anjaam aur apni sab aarzooe’n yahan tak keh mujhe maut aa jaaye. Aap par salaam ho Khuda ki rehmat ho aur uski barkaat ho aur Muhammad (s.a.w.a) par aur unki nek Aal (a.s) par Khuda rehmat farmaaye.", "Urdu": "آپ پر سلام ہو اے ابو عبداللہ ؑ!آپ وہ دروازہ ہیں جس سے خدا دیتا ہے اور وہاں سے لیا جاتاہے میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ آپ نے حق بیان کیا آپ نے ہمیشہ سچ بولا اور میرے اور اپنے مولا کی طرف بلاتے رہے ظاہراورپوشیدہ طور پر میں آیا ہوں آپ کی زیارت کرنے اور اپنی حاجات آپ کے سپرد کرنےکے لئے اب میں آپ سے وداع ہوتا ہوں آپ کے سپرد کیا میں نے اپنا دین اپنی امانت اپنے عمل کا انجام اور اپنی سب آرزوئیں یہاں تک کہ مجھے موت آجائے آپ پر سلام ہوخدا کی رحمت ہو اور اس کی برکات ہوں اور محمدؐ پر اور ان کی نیک آل ؑ پر خدا رحمت فرمائے۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA ABAA A’BDIL LAAHE ANTA BAABUL LAAHIL MOA-TAA MINHO WAL-MAAKHOOZO A’NHO ASH-HADO ANNAKA QULTA HAQQAN WA NATAQTA SIDQAN WA DA-A’WTA ILAA MAWLAAYA WA MAWLAAKA A’LAANIYYATAN WA SIRRAN ATAYTOKA ZAAA-ERAN WA HAAJAATEE LAKA MUSTAWDE-A’N WA HAA ANAA ZAA MOWAD-DE-O’KA ASTAWDE-O’KA DEENEE WA AMAANATEE WA KHAWAATEEMA A’MALEE WA JA-WAA-ME-A’ AMALEE MUNTAHAA AJALEE WAS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU WA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALEHIL AKHYAAR.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا اَبَا عَبْدِ اللہِ اَنْتَ بَابُ اللہِ الْمُؤْتٰی مِنْهُ وَالْمَاْخُوْذُ عَنْهُ۔ اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ قُلْتَ حَقًّا وَنَطَقْتَ صِدْقًا وَدَعَوْتَ اِلٰی مَوْلَایَ وَمَوْلَاكَ عَلَانِیَّۃً وَسِرًّا اَتَیْتُكَ زَآئِرًا وَحَاجَاتِیْ لَكَ مُسْتَوْدِعًا وَهَا اَنَا ذَا مُوَدِّعُكَ اَسْتَوْدِعُكَ دِیْنِیْ وَاَمَانَتِیْ وَخَوَاتِیْمَ عَمَلِیْ وَجَوَامِعَ اَمَلِیْ اِلٰی مُنْتَهٰی اَجَلِیْ وَالسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ وَصَلَّی اللہُ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِهِ الْاَخْیَارِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, 